### Number of unique meditation outputs possible right now

Practically:

* 8 meditation categories
* Same 7-step structure
* Same durations
* Same writing style
* Optional name insertion
* Optional focus insertion

So the system currently produces **8 core meditation templates**, not hundreds or thousands of unique meditations.

If your Figma requirement is a truly personalized AI meditation generator, this file is only a **static placeholder/fallback implementation**. The comments at the top indicate the developers planned to later connect it to OpenAI/Gemini:

```python
